Class ClassSchedule

java.lang.Object
com.example.project3.ClassSchedule
public class ClassSchedule extends Object
A class that manage multiple fitness classes. This class can return with fitness classes information and print out information of the memeber checked in.
Author:
Sihua Zhou, Yihang Sun
